{
  "id": "6953babb79f8f33e2377778c",
  "title": "垂直タブバー",
  "created": 1767094976,
  "updated": 1773412960,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6953babb79f8f33e2377778c",
      "text": "垂直タブバー",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1767094976,
      "updated": 1767094976
    },
    {
      "id": "6953babf0000000000f16d61",
      "text": "[タブ]を横展開ではなく[縦展開]（[垂直展開]）するタイプの[タブバー]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1767094976,
      "updated": 1767095009
    },
    {
      "id": "69b41da7000000000041b44a",
      "text": "　[row型タブバー]という呼称のほうが分かりやすいのではないかと思ってる[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1773411752,
      "updated": 1773411817
    },
    {
      "id": "69b41e23000000000041b44b",
      "text": "　あるいは[リスト型タブバー]とか[Nrem.icon]",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1773411875,
      "updated": 1773411899
    },
    {
      "id": "69b41e53000000000041b44c",
      "text": "　　垂直タブというと本の背表紙みたいなものを指している可能性が排除できないので、慣習的に伝わらない可能性があるソフトウェアの翻訳で悩んだ",
      "userId": "6780c5dd585ee07f1dc50b2b",
      "created": 1773411924,
      "updated": 1773412003
    },
    {
      "id": "6953bac40000000000f16d62",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1767094981,
      "updated": 1767094981
    },
    {
      "id": "6953bae50000000000f16d64",
      "text": "[Chromium系ブラウザ]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1767095014,
      "updated": 1767095022
    },
    {
      "id": "6953baef0000000000f16d66",
      "text": "\t[Chromium]：実装中",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1767095024,
      "updated": 1773411645
    },
    {
      "id": "6953baf60000000000f16d67",
      "text": "\t[Chrome]：実装中",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1767095031,
      "updated": 1773411692
    },
    {
      "id": "69b4225000000000005bc618",
      "text": "\t\t[Chromeの垂直タブバー]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1773412945,
      "updated": 1773412948
    },
    {
      "id": "6953bafb0000000000f16d68",
      "text": "\t[Microsoft Edge]：利用可能",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1767095036,
      "updated": 1767095048
    },
    {
      "id": "6953bae60000000000f16d65",
      "text": "\t[Vivaldi]：利用可能",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1767095015,
      "updated": 1767095063
    },
    {
      "id": "6953bb0f0000000000f16d69",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1767095056,
      "updated": 1767095056
    },
    {
      "id": "6953bb190000000000f16d6a",
      "text": "[Firefox系ブラウザ]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1767095066,
      "updated": 1767095217
    },
    {
      "id": "6953bbb00000000000f16d6c",
      "text": "\t[Firefox]：利用可能",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1767095218,
      "updated": 1767095228
    },
